name: Power Master 1 - Fora Temple Unity Alpha Build
name_original: Power Master 1 - Fora Temple Unity Alpha Build
description:
The old and unfinished build of Power Master 1's Fora Temple, built using the Unity 3D engine. Now uploaded for your enjoyment!

Move using the arrow or WASD keys, look with the mouse, and jump with the spacebar.

Play the final game here!
